    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Your sarcasm isn't necessary. We've reviewed the data, and it's clear your algorithms have been disproportionately flagging candidates from specific ethnic backgrounds as \"high risk\" for failing out. The board believes a human panel can look past the numbers to see the lived experience and potential of those students. We need to ensure our admissions aren't just numbers-driven, but equitable.",
